  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网的数据流图。核心是从边缘节点采集数据，经过PLC逻辑处理，最终控制执行器。我先梳理一下关键组件：EdgeNode作为数据采集端，MQTT Broker做消息中转，PLC Logic负责逻辑判断，ActuatorController是最终执行单元。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到了EdgeNode，后面是否还需要区分不同的边缘节点？比如一个用于审计追溯，一个用于实时数据采集？另外数据流的方向是单向还是双向？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，需要两个EdgeNode实例。Audit节点专门做审计日志，Define节点负责实时数据定义和预处理。数据流大部分是单向的，但PLC和Broker之间需要双向通信——PLC既发布状态也订阅控制指令。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出四个核心节点：Audit、Define两个EdgeNode，Barg作为PLC Logic，Bail作为MQTT Broker。然后连上Audit到Define的数据流，以及Define到Barg的预处理流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加上ActuatorController，我内部叫它Code。它接收Define节点的指令，但有个问题——Code不能直接连Define，中间需要经过Barg的决策逻辑。另外Broker和PLC之间是双向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code节点，连接Code到Define。Barg和Bail之间画上双向箭头。这样结构是：Audit→Define→Barg↔Bail，同时Code→Define。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "方向反了，Code应该是从Define接收指令，不是Code指向Define。应该是Define指向Code，或者Code从Define获取？不对，让我重新说——Code是执行器，它要上报状态给Define，所以是Code→Define没错。但Barg到Bail的箭头方向我需要确认：Barg发布到Bail，Bail也发控制给Barg，双向是对的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Code→Define表示执行器上报状态到边缘节点。那Barg和Bail的双向，是Barg→Bail和Bail→Barg都要单独标出吗？另外，是否还有Risk和Signal这些节点？看您之前的材料里有提到。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，补上Risk和Signal。Risk是风险检测模块，它输出Signal信号给Barg。还有Place和Press，Place是物理位置传感器，输出Press压力信号。这些属于辅助数据流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "添加Risk、Signal、Place、Press四个节点。连接Risk→Signal，Signal→Barg，Place→Press。Press后面需要连到哪里吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Press暂时作为独立输出，不连到主链路。整个图检查一遍：Audit和Define都是EdgeNode，Bail是Broker，Barg是PLC，Code是ActuatorController。数据流：Audit→Define→Barg↔Bail，Code→Define，Risk→Signal→Barg，Place→Press。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Code",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认完毕。所有节点和关系已对齐：两个EdgeNode实例（Audit/Define）、MQTT Broker（Bail）、PLC Logic（Barg）、ActuatorController（Code），加上Risk-Signal和Place-Press两条辅助链路。布局采用从左到右的flowchart LR结构。",
